{
  "stem": "14737.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Come in camp, bloody noses, bloody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This I've seen myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We've been in Kiev about three, four days, I find myself-- there's nowhere to escape here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, can you image the escape?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can escape, because I speak Ukraine, but where I'm going to escape in a city?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now the sergeant who was in charge of our unit was a drunk man, but me considered that I am a poor accountant in the Carpathian, he made me like I was his servant also.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was with me more less harsh. he did-- the other thing he was beating up, and [INAUDIBLE] still was this hanging, and all kinds.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not going to tell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK, another story I forgot-- before we went to the Soviet-occupied territories, it was a Sunday, they allowed the women and men who had come to say good bye, but they didn't let them in.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They brought packages, they didn't let him in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This sergeant who got drunk-- I cannot go in all these stories.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm in Kiev.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, there's a roll call and they take 30 people from the roll call where I am.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this sergeant [NON-ENGLISH] tells that he wants-- he wants me, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They take me out on another roll call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wants me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I should go with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I go with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They line us up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They walking.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're going someplace.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know where, where they take me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Finally, the destination was [NON-ENGLISH] It's from Kiev not far, the first city, the first place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] was normal from World War I, there was a place that there are a lot of POWs there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was known even before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I never heard about it by then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And taking us though the [NON-ENGLISH]-- the river.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
